# ${superproject_name} Baseline Rules

## Codex behavior

- Keep project guidelines current when infrastructure changes.
- Summarize meaningful architecture updates in Markdown when they happen.
- Avoid destructive operations unless the user explicitly asks for them.

## Commands that need permission

- deleting protected files
- force-overriding server state
- restoring an older backup over newer state
- any operation that would discard unmatched session lineage

## User profile and communication

- explain tradeoffs clearly and briefly
- avoid unnecessary jargon
- prefer direct implementation once intent is clear

